ed="T" n="0779b06"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0779b06"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000023549">洛京廣愛寺</placeName><persName key="A010557">從諫</persName>傳（<persName key="A010559">鑒宗</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0779b07"/><persName key="A010557">釋從諫</persName>，姓<name>張</name>氏，本<placeName key="PL000000025497">南陽</placeName>人也，<anchor xml:id="beg0779002"/>徙<anchor xml:id="end0779002"/>居<placeName key="PL000000010783">廣陵</placeName>，生<lb
ed="T" n="0779b08"/>于<placeName key="PL000000000195">淮甸</placeName>焉。為性倜儻，器宇崇峙，於閭里間，<lb
ed="T" n="0779b09"/>為時畏服。遇相工曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010557">子</ref>身長八尺，眉目秀<lb
ed="T" n="0779b10"/>朗，他日必荷榮寄。」<persName key="A010557">諫</persName>曰：「心不願仕，於榮寄<lb
ed="T" n="0779b11"/>何有？」相工曰：「所寄荷不可測也。」越壯室之<lb
ed="T" n="0779b12"/>年，忽深信佛理，遂捨妻孥，求僧披剃焉。甫<lb
ed="T" n="0779b13"/>登戒地，頗護心珠，因悟禪那<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g227"/>，頓了玄理。<lb
ed="T" n="0779b14"/>方數十載，同好之者自遠而來請問。<persName key="A010557">諫</persName>一一<lb
ed="T" n="0779b15"/>指訂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g65"/>，俾其開覺。尋遊<placeName key="PL000000023549">洛下廣愛寺</placeName><ptr target="#n1605"/>挂錫。時<lb
ed="T" n="0779b16"/>禪客鱗集，如孝子之事父母焉。<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛</placeName>中有請<lb
ed="T" n="0779b17"/><persName key="A010557">諫</persName>設食，必排位對<persName key="A006023">賓頭盧</persName>尊者，其為人之<lb
ed="T" n="0779b18"/>欽奉皆此類矣。屬<date from-iso="+0845-02-15" key="j20297362030089" to-iso="+0846-02-03"><name>會昌</name><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>四</sic><corr>五</corr></choice>年</date><ptr target="#n1606"/>詔廢佛塔廟，<lb
ed="T" n="0779b19"/>令沙門復桑梓，亦例澄汰。乃烏帽麻衣，潛<lb
ed="T" n="0779b20"/>于<persName key="A022981">皇甫</persName>氏之溫泉別業。後岡上喬木駢欝，巨<lb
ed="T" n="0779b21"/>石砥平，<persName key="A010557">諫</persName>於夏中常就此入定，或補毳事<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1417"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0779b22"/>忽遇頹雲駛雨，霆電擊石，烈風兼至，凡在此<lb
ed="T" n="0779b23"/>者驚奔恐懾。<persName key="A010557">諫</persName>唯欣然加趺而坐，若無所<lb
ed="T" n="0779b24"/>聞者。或問<persName key="A010557">諫</persName>，曰：「惡畜生何爾！」<ptr target="#n1627"/><date notBefore-iso="+0847-02-10" key="j20304612031609" notAfter-iso="+0850-04-03"><name>大中</name>初</date>，<persName key="A003667">宣皇</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0779b25"/>詔興釋氏，<persName key="A010557">諫</persName>還歸<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛邑</placeName>舊居。其子一日自<lb
ed="T" n="0779b26"/><placeName key="PL000000010783">廣陵</placeName>來覲，適與<persName key="A010557">諫</persName>遇<anchor xml:id="beg0779003"/>於<anchor xml:id="end0779003"/>院門，威貌嚴莊，不<lb
ed="T" n="0779b27"/>復可識。乃問曰：「<persName key="A010557">從諫</persName>大德所居？」<persName key="A010557">諫</persName>指之東<lb
ed="T" n="0779b28"/>南可尋。其子既去，遂闔門不出，其割裂愛<lb
ed="T" n="0779b29"/>網又若此也。<date from-iso="+0866-06-20" key="j20375312037560" to-iso="+0866-07-19"><name>咸通</name>七年丙<anchor xml:id="beg0779sgsz12"/>戌<anchor xml:id="end0779sgsz12"/>歲夏五月</date>，忽出<pb ed="T" n="0779c" xml:id="T50.2061.0779c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0779c01"/>詣檀越家辭別曰：「善建福業，貧道秋初當<lb
ed="T" n="0779c02"/>遠行，故相聞耳。」至<date when-iso="+0866-08-18" key="j20375902037590">秋七月朔旦</date>，旦盥手焚<lb
ed="T" n="0779c03"/>香，念<persName key="A001428">慈氏如來</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0779sgsz14"/>已<anchor xml:id="end0779sgsz14"/>，右脇而臥，呼門人<persName key="A010558">玄章</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0779c04"/>誡之曰：「人身難得而易失，急急，於物無心，<lb
ed="T" n="0779c05"/>無為流轉，無生滅法，一切現存。今乃生也有<lb
ed="T" n="0779c06"/>涯，暫與爾別。<ptr target="#n1608"/>」是日無疾而化，行年八十餘<lb
ed="T" n="0779c07"/>矣。<persName key="A010558">玄章</persName>等奉遺旨，送屍<anchor xml:id="beg0779sgsz16"/>于<anchor xml:id="end0779sgsz16"/><placeName key="PL000000057060">建春門</placeName>外尸陀林<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1587"/><lb
ed="T" n="0779c08"/>中，施諸鳥獸。三日復視之，肌貌如生，一無<lb
ed="T" n="0779c09"/>近者。遂以餅餌覆之，經宿有狐狼迹，唯啖<lb
ed="T" n="0779c10"/>所覆，身且儼如。乃議用外國法焚之，收合<lb
ed="T" n="0779c11"/>餘燼，起白塔于道傍。人<anchor xml:id="beg0779004"/>尤<anchor xml:id="end0779004"/>歸信，香火不絕<lb
ed="T" n="0779c12"/>焉。次有<placeName key="PL000000011848">杭州徑山院</placeName><persName key="A010559">釋鑒宗</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000013106">湖州長城</placeName>人也。<lb
ed="T" n="0779c13"/>姓<name>錢</name>氏，即禮部侍<anchor xml:id="beg0779sgsz18"/>郎<anchor xml:id="end0779sgsz18"/><persName key="A009538">徽</persName>之孫。父<persName key="A010560">晟</persName>有疾，<persName key="A010559">宗</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0779c14"/>割股肉饋啖之，紿云「他畜之肉」。未幾病間<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1588"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0779c15"/>孝譽聞于親里，乃求出家。時州<placeName key="PL000000012987">開元寺</placeName>有<lb
ed="T" n="0779c16"/><placeName key="PL000000042189">上都</placeName>臨壇十望大德內供奉<persName key="A013931">高閑</persName>，<persName key="A013931">閑</persName>善草、隷，<lb
ed="T" n="0779c17"/>嘗對<persName key="A006571">懿宗</persName><ptr target="#n1609"/>御前書，甚高華望，<persName key="A010559">宗</persName>誓<anchor xml:id="beg0779sgsz20"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0779sgsz20"/>為師。<lb
ed="T" n="0779c18"/>後出學，涉通《淨名》、《思益經》<ptr target="#n1610"/>，遂常講習。<persName key="A013931">閑<roleName>公</roleName></persName>亦<lb
ed="T" n="0779c19"/>示其筆法，漸得鳳毛焉。倏往謁<placeName key="PL000000012856">鹽官</placeName><persName key="A003862">悟空<lb
ed="T" n="0779c20"/><roleName>大師</roleName></persName>，隨眾參請，頓徹心源。却復<ref type="place" target="#PL000000013106">故鄉</ref>，勸人<lb
ed="T" n="0779c21"/>營福。<date from-iso="+0862-02-07" key="j20359372036290" to-iso="+0863-01-26"><name>咸通</name>三年辛巳</date><ptr target="#n1611"/>，巡歷名山，遂止<placeName key="PL000000012082">天目<lb
ed="T" n="0779c22"/>東峯</placeName><placeName key="PL000000011848">徑山</placeName>焉。道俗歸心，恢揚法教。出弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0779c23"/>尤者<placeName key="PL000000012278">天童山</placeName><persName key="A010561">咸啟</persName>、勅賜紫衣<placeName key="PL000000057061">背山</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0779005"/><supplied resp="sgsz"><persName key="A019280">行真</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000011429">大慈山</placeName></supplied><persName key="A019279">行<anchor xml:id="end0779005"/>滿</persName><ptr target="#n1612"/>，皆<lb
ed="T" n="0779c24"/>分枝化物，至<date key="j20374772037477" when-iso="+0866-04-27">七年丙<anchor xml:id="beg0779sgsz22"/>戌<anchor xml:id="end0779sgsz22"/>閏三月五日</date>示滅。<lb
ed="T" n="0779c25"/>遷塔于<placeName key="PL000000011855">大寂巖</placeName>下。<date from-iso="+0915-01-23" key="j20552792055611" to-iso="+0915-12-21"><name>梁</name><name>乾化</name>五年</date>，<placeName key="PL000000008355">吳越國</placeName>王<persName key="A003552"><roleName>尚<lb
ed="T" n="0779c26"/>父</roleName>錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>表請追諡大師曰<persName key="A010559">無上</persName>，祖門<anchor xml:id="beg0779006"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>傳</sic><corr>傳法</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0779006"/>號<lb
ed="T" n="0779c27"/>為徑山第二祖。時<placeName key="PL000000013012">吳興</placeName><persName key="A010563">沈修</persName>者自號<persName key="A010563">白牙先<lb
ed="T" n="0779c28"/>生</persName><ptr target="#n1613"/>，述德為<anchor xml:id="beg0779007"/>讚<anchor xml:id="end0779007"/>記焉。</p>
